<br>
Procs do not stop a pet from attacking. Epic pet can and has (in my sight) procced 3 or 4 swings in a single 'round' of attacks. In a row. At once. No delay between them. The Sword of Runes is no different in that if the pet procs on a target, any other swings that round will be as they always were. Procs are Procs, no matter that it's on a weapon or not. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886">Rhasin Firestorm</A><BR>
